data.description: Beautiful home in University Gardens located on a corner lot. This home has an above pool with a new deck and 3 large bedrooms. The living rooms has a welcoming fireplace, large kitchen with granite countertops. It also has a formal dining room.This has a VA assumable loan if qualified  with a great interest rate! Nice two car garage and large back yard. Don;t miss out on this one! Updated master bathroom!Call a realtor today!!!!
